    "role": "Survivor",
    "img": "Orion/wiretap",
    "character": "Ada Wong",
    "description": "\u003cp\u003eYou know that the best way to stay one step ahead is to keep tabs on the competition.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eWiretap\u003c/i\u003e activates after completing a total of \u003cspan class=\"Highlight1\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-1\"\u003e33\u003c/span\u003e%\u003c/span\u003e worth of repair progress on generators. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAfter repairing a Generator for at least \u003cspan class=\"Highlight2\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-1\"\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e seconds\u003c/span\u003e, press the \u003ci\u003eActive Ability button 1\u003c/i\u003e to install a Wiretap, which stays active for \u003cspan class=\"Highlight3\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-1\"\u003e60\u003c/span\u003e/\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-2\"\u003e70\u003c/span\u003e/\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-3\"\u003e80\u003c/span\u003e seconds\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Aura of trapped generators are revealed in yellow to all Survivors.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen the Killer enters within \u003cspan class=\"Highlight4\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tunable level-1\"\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e meters\u003c/span\u003e of the trapped generator, their aura is revealed to all Survivors. Damaging the generator destroys the trap.\u003c/p\u003e"
